Victor Rodman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victor_Rodman 0 Victor Rodman (born Victor Rottman, August 6, 1892–June 29, 1965) was an American actor best known for his work on two Jack Webb NBC television programs, Dragnet and Noah's Ark.
